{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC15_TAN_520.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1d,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "(That's right, I made a promise to Tanya.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "(I wonder if I can find something that she might like...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, are you looking for something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Ah, yes. I wanted to get a gift for this girl that I know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "She lives way beyond Hornheim and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I was wondering what would be a nice city-ish souvenir."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "City-ish? I've never heard of that before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But, let's see... If your friend is a girl, maybe clothes, perfume, or something small..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure she'll like an accessory."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, well it's just a gift, so I don't want anything too expensive or she might get worried."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Then...what about an embroidered handkerchief? It's also scented and it looks really cute."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that is cute! I think Tanya would love it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, Tanya...who lives beyond<CR>Hornheim..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Well, the handkerchief it is! I'll wrap it up right away, so please hold on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "All done.<CR>Here you go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Oh, how much is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Don't worry about it.<CR>It's on me this time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "In exchange, can you give her a message?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6d,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Tell her, \"Thank you for all the salt.<CR>I use it all the time.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Do you know Tanya, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I recognized her name. I've only seen it on invoices, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "She's the daughter of one of our vendors. Sometimes the packages are delivered with her name as the sender."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Plus, not many people live beyond Hornheim, so I just guessed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I see... Tanya really admires the city."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I know the feeling. When you live in a rural area, you always admire city life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Just listening to the stories makes you think that the city is a fun and sparkly place."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I think...I know the feeling, too. Although, I liked the rural life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, she's a regular patron,<CR>so let me do this favor for her."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I understand. Thank you for the handkerchief."
        }
    ]
}